metadata.dc:description: Presentation of 2 case reports of female patients with vaginal metastasis from renal adenocarcinoma presenting genitorrhage which was part of a polymetastatic picture. Discussion of the clinical, diagnostic and prognostic aspects of this disease.
metadata.dc:title: Metástasis vaginal de un adenocarcinoma renal: presentación de 2 casos clínicos.
[Vaginal metastasis of renal adenocarcinoma: report of 2 clinical cases].
